=== 評價 ===

[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的58篇專業影評文章中，有50篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為86%，平均得分6.9分（滿分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain_underpants_the_first_epic_movie|title=Captain Underpants: The First Epic Movie (2017)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2017-06-02|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113140220/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/captain_underpants_the_first_epic_movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的20篇評論文章，其中15篇予以好評，1篇差評，4篇褒貶不一，平均分為70（滿分100），綜合結果為「普遍良好的評價」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/captain-underpants-the-first-epic-movie|title=Captain Underpants: The First Epic Movie reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2017-06-02|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111191924/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/captain-underpants-the-first-epic-movie|dead-url=no}}</ref>。據[[影院評分|CinemaScore]]所進行的調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B+」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/06/wonder-woman-captain-underpants-weekend-box-office-opening-1202106462/|title=‘Wonder Woman’ Prevails On Thursday With $11M; Best Preview Night For A Movie By Female Director|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-06-02|accessdate=2017-06-03|archive-date=2017-06-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qzAqA9q3?url=http://deadline.com/2017/06/wonder-woman-captain-underpants-weekend-box-office-opening-1202106462/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
在北美，本片與《[[神力女超人_(2017年電影)|神力女超人]]》同時上映競爭，估計在首週末能從三千四百多間戲院中獲得2000萬美元左右的票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/05/wonder-woman-box-office-opening-worldwide-projection-gal-gadot-1202104439/|title=‘Wonder Woman’: All The World Is Waiting For You As Warner Bros./DC Pic Eyes $175M+ Global Opening|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|publisher=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-05-30|accessdate=2017-06-03|archive-date=2017-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170531011207/http://deadline.com/2017/05/wonder-woman-box-office-opening-worldwide-projection-gal-gadot-1202104439/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週末票房為2350萬美元，位居當週亞軍<ref name=opening>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2017/06/wonder-woman-captain-underpants-weekend-box-office-opening-1202106462/|title=‘Wonder Woman’ Breaks Glass Ceiling For Female Directors & Stomps On ‘Iron Man’ With $100.5M Debut – Sunday AM Final|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2017-06-04|accessdate=2017-06-03|archive-date=2017-06-05|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6qzAqA9q3?url=http://deadline.com/2017/06/wonder-woman-captain-underpants-weekend-box-office-opening-1202106462/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

